	   <tr><td colspan=1 id=headerrow>Posted @ Fri, Aug 18th 2:55 AM 2000</td>
	   <td id=headerrow align=right><span id=notbold>Score</span>: Good<span id=notbold>[4.40]</span></td></tr>
	   <tr><td colspan=2>As a cleric in Fadwer heres' some reccomendations for soloing <br><br>1 - 4 Bugs n snakes n baby mobs, chicks, welps etc<br>4 - 8 Tower,Druidring and Gnome Skeletons<br>8 - 12 Chessboard<br>12 - 18 Unrest Yard trash<br>18 - 22 Crocs n Drybones n Ghouls in Oasis / Ro<br>22 - 25 Third floor of Befallen<br>25 - 30 Giant Skeletons in Rathe lake n Mntn<br>30 - 40 Unrest again in the House at Bloodpool<br>35 - 45 Specters in Oasis and Feerot and Emerald Jungle Plaguebones n Tatterbacks(undead gorilla's)<br>40 - 50 Lower Guk&nbsp;&nbsp;ahh Heck 40 - 60<br><br>Just some of the places I enjoyed levels are approximate as its been a while.. <br><br><br><br><br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
