	   <tr><td colspan=2><br>One more thing that I wasn't clear on.&nbsp;&nbsp;Mana efficiency is more important for your class than any other.  You should always know how many heals you have left, how many you have to start, and how long it will take to med up for another heal.  It can sometimes get that close.  <br><br> The cleric buffs also, are the best for Ac/hp.  Don't be stingy with the symbol buffs, just accept it as an expense and use it on the tanks.  They are the ones that will taunt multiple mobs to beat on them to keep you free to cast.  So give those tanks the extra buffer of hps they need.  <br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
